=== SYMBIOTE_OFFER ===
# id: 27
# title: The Symbiote's Offer
# chinese_title: 共生体
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

A small, slug-like creature emerges from a ventilation shaft and inches toward you. Its skin shifts colors to match your uniform. Your scanner identifies it as a neural symbiote — harmless, possibly beneficial. It extends a tendril toward your hand, waiting for permission.

* [Allow the symbiote to bond with you]
  ~ gain_radical("虫")
  "虫" (chóng) — insect, bug, creature
* [Offer it food instead of bonding]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "喂" (wèi) — to feed
* [Capture it for study]
  ~ gain_item("biogel_patch")
  "捕" (bǔ) — to capture, to catch
* [Shoo it away gently]
  ~ nothing
  "去" (qù) — to go, to leave
